---
<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:items-center">
        <div class="relative flex-1 reveal">
            <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2474661/pexels-photo-2474661.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" 
                alt="Authentic Kerala Spices and Food" 
                class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover aspect-[4/3]"
                loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute -bottom-4 right-4 md:right-8 bg-[#dca43b] text-[#1e4a30] py-3 px-5 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center">
                <span class="block text-lg tracking-widest font-bold">★★★★★</span>
                <span class="font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">Rated 5 Stars</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 reveal delay-1">
            <span class="inline-block text-[#c75438] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[3px] text-xs mb-4">Our Heritage</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-heading text-[#1e4a30] leading-tight mb-5">A Symphony of Spices in Hamilton</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed">At Mallu's Corner, we don't just serve food — we serve a piece of our home. Every dish is a tribute to the rich culinary legacy of Kerala, prepared with hand-picked spices.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed">Whether you crave authentic South Indian delicacies, perfectly spiced Chinese fusion, or aromatic Arabic dishes, our chefs ensure an unforgettable experience.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#f1ebd9] text-[#1e4a30] px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">🌿 Kerala Spices</span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#f1ebd9] text-[#1e4a30] px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">🌶️ Indo-Chinese</span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#f1ebd9] text-[#1e4a30] px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">👨‍🍳 Expert Chefs</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
